io.micronaut.scheduling.instrument

Interface InstrumentedExecutorService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.concurrent.Executor, java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService, InstrumentedExecutor, RunnableInstrumenter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    InstrumentedScheduledExecutorService

    public interface InstrumentedExecutorService
extends java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService, InstrumentedExecutor
    An ExecutorService that has been instrumented to allow for propagation of thread state and other instrumentation related tasks.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Graeme Rocher
